### NotificationAPI Test Requests
### Base URL - Update port based on your Aspire configuration
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7XXX
@adminToken = your-jwt-token-here

### Health Check (No Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Get All Pending Notifications (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Notifications for Hotel 1 (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/hotel/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Notifications for Hotel 2 (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/hotel/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Notification by ID (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Manually Trigger Low Capacity Check (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/trigger/low-capacity-check
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Manually Trigger Reservation Processing (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/trigger/process-reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Test Without Authorization (Should Return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/pending

###
